    <string name="help_faq_create_entry_q">How do I create an entry?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_create_entry_a">Tap the + button on the journal screen. Add a title, location, date, photos, mood, and tags — or just a title and a few words. Everything saves automatically.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_swipe_entries_q">How do I swipe between entries?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_swipe_entries_a">On the journal list, swipe left or right anywhere on an entry card to move to the next or previous memory. The counter at the top shows your position.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_adventures_map_q">What is the Adventures map?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_adventures_map_a">The Adventures map plots every location you\'ve journalled on a world map. Tap the globe icon on the journal screen to open it. Pins group by city — tap a cluster to zoom in.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_reset_password_q">How do I reset my password?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_reset_password_a">On the login screen, tap \"Forgot password?\" and enter your email. You\'ll receive a reset link in a few seconds. This only applies to email/password accounts — if you signed in with Google, use your Google account to manage your password.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_reorder_photos_q">How do I reorder or remove photos?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_reorder_photos_a">Open the entry in edit mode. Long-press any photo and drag it to a new position to reorder. Tap the × on a photo to remove it from the entry (the photo stays in your gallery).</string>
    <string name="help_faq_use_tags_q">How do I use tags?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_use_tags_a">Type a tag in the entry editor and press the + button to add it. Tags let you group entries by trip, theme, or any label you like. Tap a tag chip on any entry in the journal list to filter by that tag.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_transfer_device_q">Transfer to a new device</string>
    <string name="help_faq_transfer_device_a">Sign in with the same Google or email account on your new device. Your entries sync automatically within a few seconds. Photos saved via Backup &amp; Restore will also restore once you re-import the backup file.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_premium_benefits_q">What do I get with premium?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_premium_benefits_a">Premium unlocks the full Macaco experience: unlimited journal entries, the Adventures map, swipe between entries, custom themes, and priority support. Available as Monthly, Annual, or Lifetime.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_premium_broken_q">Premium not working?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_premium_broken_a">Try restoring your purchase: open Settings, scroll to Subscription, and tap Restore purchase. Make sure you\'re signed in with the same account used when you bought. If it still doesn\'t work, contact us at houseofmmminq@gmail.com.</string>
